===中东阿拉伯国家===
印度和[[沙特阿拉伯|沙特阿拉伯]]在地区事务及贸易上有较多合作。沙特是印度最大的[[石油|石油]]供应国之一，印度是沙特的第七大贸易伙伴及第五大投资国。<ref name="CH">{{cite web |url=http://www.business-standard.com/common/storypage_c_online.php?bKeyFlag=IN&autono=38855 |title=India, Saudi Arabia to better understanding |accessdate=4 June 2008 |work=[[Business_Standard|Business Standard]] |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20081216135049/http://www.business-standard.com/common/storypage_c_online.php?bKeyFlag=IN&autono=38855 |archivedate=2008-12-16 }}</ref>

